        "description": {
            "value": "<p>The writing on your shell has evolved to become a divine script, either to a deity or to a philosophy unto itself. Depending on the spell you selected for @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Repository of Divinity], you become sanctified and gain either the holy or unholy trait (holy for @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.spells.Item.Summon Celestial], or unholy for @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.spells.Item.Summon Fiend]). Your @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.ancestry-features.Item.Fire Breath] gains the sanctified trait, and you can choose to deal spirit damage instead of fire damage.</p>"
